node.text: Happy birthday to my BFF @dr.shirisha who is the most talented person in the world!! Not only is she an amazing physician but also sings like an angel and today I wanted to share her amazing voice and talent with everyone. Ever since we first met back in residency in 2014 on an ICU night shift, we've been wanting to record something and we finally recorded this back in May. She's singing an Arabic/Hindi mash-up, and even though she doesn't speak or understand Arabic, she signs it just flawlessly!!! Music is the one true universal language. Happy birthday to you!! @samirasaid #samirasaid #سميرة_سعيد
